      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "予想通りLizNoirがグランプリ決勝戦へと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected‚ LizNoir will be",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "コマを進めました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "advancing to the Grand Prix finals!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1866.6666666666654,
          "startTime": 11.233333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.2333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……\nやったわ、葵……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "pant pant…\nWe did it‚ Aoi…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.533333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.4333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "当然だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.066666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "では明日、決勝戦で対決することになった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ let’s hear from Mana Nagase-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2333.333333333332,
          "startTime": 19.4
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1333.3333333333321,
          "startTime": 18.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "長瀬麻奈さんに抱負を語っていただきましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "about her aspirations for the match!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.933333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "……この子",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That girl…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "……雰囲気があるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…has an aura about her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――麻奈と同じステージに立ち、二人はすぐに感じ取った",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Standing on the same stage as Mana‚ they sensed it immediately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "オーラが違う。トップクラスにも、こんな子はいない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her aura was different. There wasn’t anyone like her‚ even among the top class.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "はーい、LizNoirの神崎さん、井川さん\n決勝進出おめでとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ Kanzaki-san‚ Igawa-san of LizNoir‚\ncongratulations on making it to the finals!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.333333333333336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "明日はファンのみなさんに、沢山楽しんでいただける\n最高のライブにしましょうね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s make tomorrow’s live\nthe best live for everyone to enjoy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "麻奈！　麻奈！　ぶっちぎりで優勝だああああっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana! Mana! A landslide victoryyyy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 47.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.266666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "LizNoirーぅっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoirーooh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 52.266666666666666
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ファンB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "新人なんか蹴散らしてやれーっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Crush the newbieー!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.43333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "凄い熱気です！　優勝は若手ナンバーワンの実力派",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What an incredible atmosphere! The winner will be either the most skilled of the younger generation‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "リズノワか、彗星のごとく現れた天才、長瀬麻奈か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir‚ or the genius who appeared like a comet‚ Mana Nagase…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.2
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "明日の決勝戦は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tomorrow’s finals",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 799.9999999999972,
          "startTime": 67.73333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "きっとグランプリ史に残る名勝負となるでしょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…will surely be a legendary match that will go down in Grand Prix history!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "あーっ、すっごいあおってくるよね\nあの司会者さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah~‚ that emcee is really\ntrying to rile us up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私達は明日は仲良くやろうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But let’s be friends tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "敵と仲良くする気なんてないわ！　貴方どうして\nそんなに余裕があるのよ！？　馬鹿にしてるの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have no intention of being friends with the enemy! Why\nare you so relaxed!? Are you looking down on me!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――敵対心むき出しの言葉に一瞬きょとんとした麻奈は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Mana‚ momentarily taken aback by the words filled with hostility‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "笑顔を浮かべ、莉央が思いがけない言葉を言い放った",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…smiles‚ and then utters words that Rio had never expected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "え？　ああ、そっか\nごめんそうだね、私達、明日戦うんだったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Oh‚ right.\nSorry‚ that’s right. We’re fighting tomorrow‚ aren’t we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "すっかり忘れてた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I completely forgot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
